@tfboyd Nice to know but the problem is that [super blending edge/fresh solutions](https://github.com/tensorflow/models/tree/master/research/deeplab) are still contributed with SLIM from the "internal" flow pipeline.
It is hard to know when this projects was started so I don't know what is your internal policy now.
I mentioned this basically related to my previous comment on https://github.com/tensorflow/models/issues/1357#issuecomment-347722179
